race.comment: SHY HI (1) turned in a moderate run last time when eighth at this track over 300m behind Noaki Uno (16.90) in a Grade 5. Has ability and can bounce back. BONNIE ROYALE (2) produced a moderate effort last time when seventh at Capalaba over 366m behind Hara's Pumpkin (20.40) in a Grade 5. The form from her last run stacks up well. A big run wouldn't surprise. KULNURA KID (6) showed good early speed but faded to a close fourth (20.35) at Capalaba over 366m. Expected to run well. FUN DAY (5) collected a minor prize last start and must be considered.
